==Bundles==
Rabbit's Foot is used in the {{Bundle|enchanter||y}}.

==Recipes==
Rabbit's Foot is not used in any recipes.

==Tailoring==
Rabbit's Foot is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create a [[Tailoring|Shirt]]. [[File:Shirt095.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
Rabbit's Foot is not used in any [[quests]].

==Other Uses==
*One Rabbit's Foot is used when solving the puzzle depicted in [[Secret Notes#Secret Note #20|Secret Note #20]].
*Having a Rabbit's Foot in inventory prevents a negative outcome in the [[Bouquet#Group 10-Heart Event|Group 10-Heart Event]].

